      <title>延参健胃胶囊-有一个中成药，能把脾胃里的寒和热都散了</title>
      <link>https://qfmy321.github.io/post/zcy/yanshengjianweijiaonang/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Sep 2023 16:01:23 +0800</pubDate><author>me@example.com (ZY)</author>
